    <item>
      <title>乌克兰寻求3000亿美元俄罗斯资产购买美国武器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/ukraine-seeks-300-billion-of-russian-assets-to-buy-us-weapons</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情的欧洲官员透露，乌克兰官员请求美国总统唐纳德·特朗普政府允许他们使用冻结的价值 3000 亿美元的俄罗斯资产购买美国制造的武器。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/ukraine-seeks-300-billion-of-russian-assets-to-buy-us-weapons</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 17:57:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普与普京同意就乌克兰战争进行会谈，美国政策发生转变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/trump-putin-agree-to-negotiate-over-ukraine-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他和俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京同意开始谈判以结束乌克兰战争，这表明美国对乌克兰冲突的政策发生了重大转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/trump-putin-agree-to-negotiate-over-ukraine-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 17:00:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国财政部长贝森特向泽连斯基提出经济伙伴关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/us-treasury-s-bessent-presents-economic-partnership-to-zelenskiy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基表示，美国财政部长斯科特·贝森特在访问基辅期间提交了一份经济伙伴关系协议草案，并讨论了乌克兰的自然资源。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/us-treasury-s-bessent-presents-economic-partnership-to-zelenskiy</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 16:54:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加巴德获参议院支持出任间谍部门负责人 誓言缩减人员规模</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/gabbard-wins-senate-backing-as-spy-chief-after-vow-to-downsize</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国参议院确认塔尔西·加巴德为下一任国家情报总监，最终赢得了主要共和党人的支持，部分原因是她有意精简该组织。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/gabbard-wins-senate-backing-as-spy-chief-after-vow-to-downsize</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 16:51:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克呼吁在反对声中发起“一波”司法弹劾</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/musk-calls-for-wave-of-judicial-impeachments-amid-pushback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克呼吁美国众议院弹劾多名阻止其政府削减成本行动的法官，这一非同寻常的言论有可能对联邦法官产生寒蝉效应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/musk-calls-for-wave-of-judicial-impeachments-amid-pushback</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 16:35:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>争吵不休的共和党人提出减税、提高债务上限的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/house-gop-takes-first-step-toward-tax-cuts-debt-limit-increase</link>
      <description><![CDATA[众议院共和党领导人周三迈出了第一步，准备实施数万亿美元的减税计划，并提高美国 36 万亿美元的债务上限，但这项计划有可能激怒党内争吵不休的派系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/house-gop-takes-first-step-toward-tax-cuts-debt-limit-increase</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 15:17:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥地利极右翼首次组阁尝试失败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/austria-s-far-right-freedom-party-says-coalition-talks-failed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[奥地利首次组建极右翼政府的尝试因联盟谈判破裂于周三宣告失败。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/austria-s-far-right-freedom-party-says-coalition-talks-failed</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 14:09:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>赫格塞斯拒绝让美国军队驻扎乌克兰并让其加入北约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/hegseth-says-nato-membership-not-realistic-outcome-for-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国防部长皮特·赫格塞斯周三在对北约盟国的演讲中对美国对乌克兰的支持作出了严厉限制，拒绝了乌克兰加入北约的愿望，并拒绝了部署美国军队以帮助保证与俄罗斯的战争停火的提议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/hegseth-says-nato-membership-not-realistic-outcome-for-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 13:52:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普控制司法部之际，阿达尼在美国建立影响力机器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/india-s-gautam-adani-builds-us-influence-machine-while-trump-reins-in-doj-cases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自美国对高塔姆·阿达尼因涉嫌贿赂而提起刑事和民事指控以来的几个月里，两个法庭的案卷均保持了平静。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/india-s-gautam-adani-builds-us-influence-machine-while-trump-reins-in-doj-cases</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 10:31:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普计划任命 Quintenz 为衍生品监管机构负责人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/trump-plans-to-pick-quintenz-as-head-of-us-derivatives-regulator</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据白宫发送给国会山的一份文件（彭博新闻社审阅了该文件），唐纳德·特朗普总统计划选择安德森·霍洛维茨旗下 a16z 加密货币部门的政策主管布莱恩·昆滕兹 (Brian Quintenz) 领导商品期货交易委员会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/trump-plans-to-pick-quintenz-as-head-of-us-derivatives-regulator</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 02:21:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
